<section id="about-page" class="about-page-section">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- About the Organization -->
        <div class="about-section">
            <h1 class="section-title">About Us</h1>
            <p>
                MaterFamilia is a non-profit organization dedicated to supporting communities by providing resources, mentorship, and opportunities for growth and development. 
                Our goal is to make a lasting impact on society by empowering individuals and fostering connections.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission Section -->
        <div class="mission-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                To empower individuals and communities by creating access to opportunities, resources, and mentorship that foster sustainable growth and a better future.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Vision Section -->
        <div class="vision-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Vision</h2>
            <p>
                Empowering female-headed households to become financially sustainable through  interventions like
                mentoring, coaching, skills development, and market access, reducing vulnerability to exploitative conditions
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- About the Founder -->
        <div class="founder-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">About the Founder</h2>
                <p>
                    Ann Ligman, the founder of MaterFamilia, has dedicated her life to helping others achieve their dreams. With a background in community development and a passion for social impact, 
                    Ann established MaterFamilia to create a platform where individuals can access resources and mentorship to transform their lives.
                </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Values -->
        <div class="values-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Core Values</h2>
            <ul class="values-list">
                <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> Upholding honesty and transparency in everything we do.</li>
                <li><strong>Empowerment:</strong> Enabling individuals to take control of their futures.</li>
                <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Building partnerships to maximize impact.</li>
                <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Driving change through creative solutions.</li>
                <li><strong>Compassion:</strong> Supporting those in need with empathy and care.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
